<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Please read this, you mis the point!</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois.cgi?Kiron of Sacred Haven">Kiron of Sacred Haven</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 12:37 p.m. 20/4/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Please read this, you mis the point!<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/datel.gif" width=46 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dateblnk.gif" width=100 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dater.gif" width=306 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/forum/veeshan.cgi?read=110" TARGET=_self>Re: The Monopoly of Banded Mail will stop! This concerns ALL citizens of Norrath (lng txt)</A> (Tybolt)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>My problem is not with him selling items at a standard fixed price that he set up, that is what I am doing myself. My problem is not that he has an arangement with several other smiths to sell armor at that fixed rate also. My problem is his idle threats to put me out of business and MOST importantly, how he tried to FORCE me into his prices. If you agree to that, then you are no better then him in my book. I think if you read this correctly, you will see my point and you will agree. I did touch other topics in this post, but that was the point I was trying to get through. Who gives ANYONE the right to FORCE their prices on you? Nobody! It is Tunare's will that I shall overcome Shirons tyranny. I can not do this on my own. All good people of Norrath need to band together. Show him that he can not control the market and he can not FORCE other smiths into his prices, that is also called extorition. I am not saying that you should buy from me, I am syaing you shouldn't by from Shiron or his associates.

<P>Thank you,
<BR>Kiron
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
